Package ch.obermuhlner.jhuge.collection.internal

Internal implementation details of ch.obermuhlner.jhuge.collection .

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IntArray
    Provides access to an array of int values.
    IntIterator
    Iterates over int values.
    IntLongArrayMap
    Provides a map where the keys are int and the values are long[].
    LongArray
    Provides access to an array of long values.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLongArray
    Abstract base class to simplify implementing a LongArray.
    HugeIntArray
    A IntArray implementation that stores the values in a MemoryManager.
    HugeIntLongArrayMap
    A map where the keys are int and the values are long[] that stores all data in a MemoryManager.
    HugeLongArray
    A LongArray implementation that stores the values in a MemoryManager.
    JavaIntArray
    A LongArray implementation that stores the values in a long[].
    JavaIntLongArrayMap
    A map where the keys are int and the values are long[] based by a standard Java Map.
    JavaLongArray
    A LongArray implementation that stores the values in a long[].
